{"tid":1103399,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"北京狗到寵物店沖涼高溫脫水死亡　狗主引述店員指沒主人吩咐不給水","createTime":"2019-04-12T11:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T14:25:44.000Z","uid":51598,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c64be86fab17142de41ac3fa88d0ac29c8407d06","tid":1103399,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/SOPOORPEKING-696x379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FSOPOORPEKING-696x379.jpg&h=1bdff292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【動物專訊】位於太子基隆街的寵物酒店及美容店HKpet Service發生懷疑人為疏忽致狗狗死亡事件，狗主鍾小姐日前帶北京狗「小明」到該店洗澡，想不到竟成永訣，狗狗因高溫脫水而死，死前曾不斷抓籠，但沒人理會，亦沒人給牠水喝，<span style=\"color: red;\">原因竟是狗主沒事前吩咐要給水</span>。鍾小姐十分傷痛，在網上憶述小明和兒子生活點滴，又想像到小明死前被關在無法開啟的籠，叫天不應叫地不聞，被「酷刑賜死」。<br />\n<br />\nHKpet Service回應本報查詢時表示，事件已交由警方處理，故不作回應。<br />\n<br />\n鍾小姐在「北京狗俱樂部」facebook群組中為狗狗「小明」伸冤，「1小時抓籠沒人安撫，沒有水，請問是來給你沖涼，還是虐待？狗命死在你手，法例不用你坐監，這種傷痛，只有主人媽媽才知道，不能容忍，不能接受。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n她透露當日下午兩時帶小明去HKpet Service沖涼，在3時多收到該店信息指狗狗沒反應後急趕回，<span style=\"color: red;\">得悉狗狗曾不斷抓籠但沒人理會，亦沒有給牠水</span>。小明到獸醫診所時已沒有心跳，打了兩支強心針也救不回，死因是高溫脫水。<br />\n<br />\n鍾小姐質問為何沒有給狗狗飲水，HKpet Service職員說沒有主人要求他們便不會提供。該店對閉路電視的說法也前後不一，職員說美容房的閉路電視壞了沒再裝上，店主在電話上卻說美容房根本沒裝閉路電視，到鍾小姐晚上和店員溝通要求開閉路電視畫面時，對方又說不懂開。<br />\n<br />\n這次事件讓鍾小姐留下重大的陰影，她其後在「北京狗俱樂部」再憶述小明這名字的由來，是因為她兒子中文成績不好，不懂寫太多筆畫的字，所以她教他作句時不要用「我」而用「小明」。因為這段經歷，她遇到這北京狗時便毫不猶豫地命名牠做小明。<br />\n<br />\n小明十分聰明，每早都會叫她兒子起床上學，「小明聽到阿仔嘅名，就定一定眼睛，然後就跑去阿仔房，我就抱他上床，他走到阿仔嘅面，用鼻聞他的面很久，叫他起床。」忠心的小明每次見到穿校服的小朋友都會定目細看，看是否她的兒子，「雖然他是我養的狗中最惡的一個，但他是最聰明的一個，真的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/56588478_10216188684684511_2415250051174498304_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F56588478_10216188684684511_2415250051174498304_n.jpg&h=276392ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/56942491_10216186053938744_7267396221759651840_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F56942491_10216186053938744_7267396221759651840_n.jpg&h=f34610b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/57062131_10216188674724262_6057604969287122944_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F57062131_10216188674724262_6057604969287122944_n.jpg&h=16274080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/56713021_10216194814637756_7696447533186285568_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F56713021_10216194814637756_7696447533186285568_n.jpg&h=f52d9e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京狗好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢D寵物酒店仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係識賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c28f90521577709d5483c4ceeb3926e553678d3","tid":1103399,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"小明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990f6bb3163c593642fa187b7d31e3858cba5923","tid":1103399,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"寵物店真係無腦<br />\n客人隻狗俾你整死<br />\n一陣人地John wick上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60f6ed2f1683f5df48c0a8102c7502927748a0f","tid":1103399,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc125c2480306d86b4a5a95d9a66d90e23a036b3","tid":1103399,"uid":235520,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"兩三個鐘唔飲水就死左?"},{"pid":"66c348eb8746ebbba445cd43a082cd775d966a84","tid":1103399,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc125c2480306d86b4a5a95d9a66d90e23a036b3","tid":1103399,"uid":235520,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"兩三個鐘唔飲水就死左?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"高溫脫水呀盲撚 <br />\n睇文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}